text_block_list.name: Kawakami Princess
text_block_list.text: Hraaaaagh! Princess coming through!

text_block_list.name: Kawakami Princess
text_block_list.text:
Yaaay, I did it! Another beautiful,<n>graceful, courageous
day—and a big<n>win!

text_block_list.name: Kawakami Princess
text_block_list.text: You've got that right! It's all<n>because—

text_block_list.name: Kawakami Princess
text_block_list.text:
—I've got my fateful partner! The<n>prince of my future is with
me!

text_block_list.name: Kawakami Princess
text_block_list.text:
The moment we bonded there was a<n>big bang of a miracle!
That's the real<n>power of a bond!
choice_data_list: Your confidence is through the roof...
Your confidence is through the roof...

text_block_list.name: Kawakami Princess
text_block_list.text:
There's no doubt about that! I learned<n>it all from Princess
Fighter!

text_block_list.name: Monólogo
text_block_list.text:
Wherever it came from, confidence is<n>always a good thing.
So long as she<n>can keep this up—

Hmph. It seems I've finally found<n>you, would-be princess.
Or should I<n>say, overconfident commoner?

text_block_list.name: Kawakami Princess
text_block_list.text: What do you mean, "would-be"?! And<n>who are you?!

text_block_list.name: Umamusume with Princess Curls
text_block_list.text: Heh... Can you not tell by my aurabrimming with princess spirit? I'm thereal princess here! And thestrongest too—my princess power isover 100 billion!

text_block_list.name: Kawakami Princess
text_block_list.text:
I don't care what your level is! I'm a<n>fantastic princess! I
even found my<n>prince!

text_block_list.name: Umamusume with Princess Curls
text_block_list.text:
Hm? A prince, you say? You don't<n>mean that trainer there,
do you?

text_block_list.name: Umamusume with Princess Curls
text_block_list.text:
Ahahaha! You're so plain, I didn't<n>even notice you! Like a
paltry piece of<n>carrot in cheap instant noodles!

text_block_list.name: Kawakami Princess
text_block_list.text:
M-my trainer is nothing of the sort!<n>My trainer's like, um...
wagyu steak<n>topped with caviar—
choice_data_list: Can we stop with the food comparisons?

text_block_list.name: Umamusume with Princess Curls
text_block_list.text: Heh... If you're so mad about it, whydon't you race me and make meshut up? I'll personally show youwhat a real princess can do!

text_block_list.name: Kawakami Princess
text_block_list.text:
I was about to say the same thing!<n>You'll take back those
words once I<n>beat the daylights out of you!

text_block_list.name: Monólogo
text_block_list.text:
(I've seen this Umamusume before.<n>She's a veteran with
some serious<n>Twinkle Series wins under her belt!)

text_block_list.name: Kawakami Princess
text_block_list.text:
Oh, don't worry! There's no way I'd<n>lose to a bully like that.
I'll leave her in<n>my dust and win the race in time for<n>tea!
choice_data_list: Let's at least come up with a plan!

text_block_list.name: Kawakami Princess
text_block_list.text:
Aw, come on. You worry way too<n>much! I don't need any
tactics or<n>anything! Because...

text_block_list.name: Kawakami Princess
text_block_list.text:
We've got the invincible power of our<n>bond! Just trust it and
wait for my<n>return!

text_block_list.name: Monólogo
text_block_list.text: My attempts to stop her go unheard.Maybe she's gotten a little tooconfident...

text_block_list.name: Kawakami Princess
text_block_list.text:
Okay! I've got a good pace now!<n>Time to cut straight
through to the<n>finish!

text_block_list.name: Monólogo
text_block_list.text:
Kawakami Princess is running in top<n>form like usual, but the
curly-haired<n>rival princess is trailing eerily close<n>behind
her.

text_block_list.name: Umamusume with Princess Curls
text_block_list.text:
Heh... Are you all talk, Kawakami?<n>What do you think a
princess is?

text_block_list.name: Kawakami Princess
text_block_list.text:
Huh?! I know exactly what a princess<n>is! Beautiful, graceful,
and<n>courageous...

text_block_list.name: Umamusume with Princess Curls
text_block_list.text:
Hahaha, mwahahaha! Don't make<n>me laugh! Here, I'll tell
you something<n>useful!

text_block_list.name: Umamusume with Princess Curls
text_block_list.text:
It's the undeniable, overwhelming<n>power to crush those
beneath<n>you—that's what makes a true<n>princess!

text_block_list.name: Kawakami Princess
text_block_list.text: Whaaat?!

text_block_list.name: Umamusume with Princess Curls
text_block_list.text: Aaahahahaha! If you'll excuse me!

text_block_list.name: Monólogo
text_block_list.text:
Kawakami tries desperately to catch<n>up, but by the end, she
finishes three<n>lengths behind.

text_block_list.name: Kawakami Princess
text_block_list.text: Pant, pant... Ugh, why?!

text_block_list.name: Umamusume with Princess Curls
text_block_list.text: Heh heh heh, aaahahahagh! Cough,cough! This is the differencebetween a real princess... and a fake!

text_block_list.name: Kawakami Princess
text_block_list.text: Waaah! It's not faaair!

text_block_list.name: Monólogo
text_block_list.text:
Kawakami Princess runs off before I<n>even have a chance to
console her...
